[B2 D4 F#4 C#5]:8 [G2 D4 F#4 B4]:8 [A2 D4 F#4 A4]:8 [G2 D4 F#4 Bb4]:8
[E2 D4 G4 B4]:8 [C#3 E4 G4 B4]:4 [F#2 C#4 F#4 A#4]:4
[B2 D4 F#4 C#5]:8 [G2 D4 F#4 B4]:8 [A2 D4 F#4 A4]:8 [G2 D4 F#4 Bb4]:8
[B2 D4 F#4 C#5]:12

track bass vel=0.72 patch=rawbass
B1:5.5 R:0.5 B1:1 F#2:1
B1:5.5 R:0.5 B1:1 F#2:1 | G1:5.5 R:0.5 G1:1 D2:1 | A1:5.5 R:0.5 A1:1 E2:1 | G1:5.5 R:0.5 G1:1 D2:1
B1:5.5 R:0.5 B1:1 F#2:1 | G1:5.5 R:0.5 G1:1 D2:1 | A1:5.5 R:0.5 A1:1 E2:1 | G1:5.5 R:0.5 G1:1 D2:1
E2:5.5 R:0.5 E2:1 B1:1 | C#2:4 F#1:4
B1:5.5 R:0.5 B1:1 F#2:1 | G1:5.5 R:0.5 G1:1 D2:1 | A1:5.5 R:0.5 A1:1 E2:1 | G1:5.5 R:0.5 G1:1 D2:1
B1:12

